#: prefs.js:42
msgid ""
"Instantly extract and copy text to your clipboard from anywhere on the "
"screen."
msgstr ""
"Toa na unakili maandishi papo hapo kwenye ubao wako wa kunakili kutoka "
"popote kwenye skrini."

#: prefs.js:53
msgid "Behavior & Shortcuts"
msgstr "Tabia & Njia za mkato"

#: prefs.js:57
msgid "Show Extracted Text Notification"
msgstr "Onyesha Arifa ya Maandishi Iliyotolewa"

#: prefs.js:58
msgid "Displays a system banner containing your copied text context."
msgstr "Huonyesha bango la mfumo lililo na muktadha wa maandishi uliyonakili."

#: prefs.js:72
msgid "Enable Extraction History"
msgstr "Washa Historia ya Uchimbaji"

#: prefs.js:73
msgid "Keep a history of up to 15 recent extractions in the context menu."
msgstr ""
"Weka historia ya hadi dondoo 15 za hivi majuzi kwenye menyu ya muktadha."

#: prefs.js:87
msgid "Keyboard Shortcut Trigger"
msgstr "Kianzisha Njia ya Mkato ya Kibodi"

#: prefs.js:88
msgid "Click to set shortcut. Press Esc to cancel, Backspace to disable."
msgstr ""
"Bofya ili kuweka njia ya mkato. Bonyeza Esc ili kughairi, Backspace ili "
"kuzima."

